    "First, an autoencoder calculates a latent space, and then a GAN is trained inside that latent space.",
    "This reduces the mode collapse and other difficulties in training a GAN and results in newly generated point clouds.",
    "One slight drawback is the required separate training for every category.",
    "We conducted a small test by introducing a latent vector, which encoded a chair with missing legs.",
    "The output was a noisy object, but all four legs were attached, Fig. 7."
